===Etymology===
{{bor|en|la|oeconomia}}, from {{der|en|grc|οἰκονομία||management of a household, administration}}, from {{m|grc|οἶκος||house}} + {{m|grc|νέμω||distribute, allocate}} (surface analysis {{confix|eco|nomy|lang=en}}). The first recorded sense of the word '''economy''', found in a work possibly composed in 1440, is “the management of economic affairs”, in this case, of a monastery.

